<li>Michael Riff. <i>The Face of Survival: Jewish Life in Eastern Europe Past and Present</i>. Valentine Mitchell, London, 1992. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0853032203" class="internal">ISBN 0-85303-220-3</a></li>
</ul>
